Class RCDCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.DiagramCell

    public class RCDCell
extends DiagramCell

    A cell in a reaction coordinate diagram. May contain a molecule such as an intermediate or transition state.

      • calcState

        void calcState()
        throws ParameterException,
               VerifyException

        ParameterException - if the state is not known
        VerifyException - if the state can't be calculated from the connected cells
